{
  "stem": "27285.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I very much wanted to go to school, to a normal school with all the children, with all the Czech children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Laura, being clever but very-- I was very upset about it-- she said no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to go to an English school, and to-- because there was no possibility to study Hebrew then or there was no Hebrew almost.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she said, you-- you are going to Palestine, so you have to study English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because Czech is no good for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I want to be like anybody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't want to be an outsider again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But she was a very clever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She put me-- and she made me study music.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, I studied piano playing with [INAUDIBLE], another survivor, and I went to an English language school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So here is my English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is the good-- the foundation of my English was already in Prague where I stayed a year.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was very hard after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not immediate contact, but I knew they were alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not know who survived and if survived then they still saw them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my uncle wrote to them, and there-- he was more grown up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was so-- I wrote to them, of course, in German, because there was, again, this problem of language, which I spoke only Czech and I lived in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my parents living in Palestine spoke German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So here we go again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as I told you, Laura was, and she-- and I thank God and her-- that she really said, this you are going to do if you like it or not, because there is no sense in you going to a Czech school now.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
